52:39.741 --> 52:40.901
Sir.

52:40.992 --> 52:42.323
(GROANS)

52:42.410 --> 52:45.152
Princess Margaret for Her Majesty the Queen.

52:45.246 --> 52:47.703
-On a secure line.
-Of course!

52:47.790 --> 52:48.825
What's taking so long?

52:48.916 --> 52:51.077
Well, I gather we have the secure line, ma'am.

52:51.169 --> 52:53.330
They're just having trouble
locating Her Majesty.

52:53.421 --> 52:55.457
What can be so difficult? She's the Queen.

52:55.548 --> 52:57.880
She's fairly conspicuous.
She can't disappear.

52:58.760 --> 53:00.546
