57:10.845 --> 57:13.928
PHILIP: "The treatment of her sister
has nowjeopardized the future

57:14.015 --> 57:16.631
"of the monarchy in Britain."

57:19.353 --> 57:20.854
(CUTLERY CLATTERS)

57:23.482 --> 57:26.849
In 48 hours, it would have passed.

57:27.403 --> 57:28.392
If you're lucky.

57:28.487 --> 57:31.229
I fear it will take longer than that
for Margaret to forgive me.

57:31.365 --> 57:33.572
She will in time, she has to.

57:35.620 --> 57:38.532
